{"type":"message_update","assistantMessageEvent":{"type":"toolcall_start","contentIndex":1,"partial":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We need to decide vote. Review evidence: Plaintiff's three evidence items establish US military operation in Caracas, with large force, aiming to capture Maduro. Defendant's CSIS says operation was narrow, law enforcement, not intended to establish territorial control. The proposition: \"The United States invaded Venezuela between Nov 3, 2025 and Jan 31, 2026... commenced a military offensive intended to establish control over any portion of Venezuela.\" Need to assess if record shows intent to establish control over any portion. Evidence does not explicitly state intent to control territory; only that they captured target and used control of corridor. So under preponderance, it's more likely not intended to establish control over territory, but a raid. Thus vote not_demonstrated.\n\nProvide concise rationale ≤3 sentences. Then call submit_council_vote.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-85b091f789e0c782","name":"mcp","arguments":{},"partialArgs":"","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openai/gpt-oss-120b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782780850695,"responseId":"gen-1782780850-Eyk08Kjf0xA99TfQE5pH"}},"message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We need to decide vote. Review evidence: Plaintiff's three evidence items establish US military operation in Caracas, with large force, aiming to capture Maduro. Defendant's CSIS says operation was narrow, law enforcement, not intended to establish territorial control. The proposition: \"The United States invaded Venezuela between Nov 3, 2025 and Jan 31, 2026... commenced a military offensive intended to establish control over any portion of Venezuela.\" Need to assess if record shows intent to establish control over any portion. Evidence does not explicitly state intent to control territory; only that they captured target and used control of corridor. So under preponderance, it's more likely not intended to establish control over territory, but a raid. Thus vote not_demonstrated.\n\nProvide concise rationale ≤3 sentences. Then call submit_council_vote.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"chatcmpl-tool-85b091f789e0c782","name":"mcp","arguments":{},"partialArgs":"","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openai/gpt-oss-120b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782780850695,"responseId":"gen-1782780850-Eyk08Kjf0xA99TfQE5pH"}}
