a Cano and AP contributors, captured as relevant text extract during plaintiff merits investigation.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.pbs.org/newshour/world/a-timeline-of-u-s-military-escalation-against-venezuela-leading-to-maduros-capture\",\"storage_name\":\"7d/7d30fcd0d9f704222f94166d25b9a1221e206e971b247a0beb4c9cee7ba25372\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"PBS/AP timeline of U.S. escalation leading to Maduro capture\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T00:41:48Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_e0e0fb921ec9_submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-e0e0fb921ec9\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-e0e0fb921ec9.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Official U.S. source describing the January 3, 2026 military operation in Caracas, Venezuela, including location, military character, planning, special operations forces, ground extraction force, and aircraft support.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T00:44:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"e0e0fb921ec90639876fb9c4c5697b4f6e3a0fd6a37b4b6befc970412f1f4687\",\"size_bytes\":3556,\"source_description\":\"U.S. Department of War / Pentagon News article by Matthew Olay, published January 3, 2026, captured as relevant text extract during AAR plaintiff merits investigation.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.war.gov/News/News-Stories/Article/Article/4370431/trump-announces-us-militarys-capture-of-maduro/\",\"storage_name\":\"e0/e0e0fb921ec90639876fb9c4c5697b4f6e3a0fd6a37b4b6befc970412f1f4687\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Official U.S. Department of War account of Operation Absolute Resolve in Caracas\"}]},\"turn\":{\"attempts_max\":3,\"attempts_remaining\":3,\"completed\":false,\"deadline\":\"2026-06-30T01:09:05.664729479Z\",\"deliberation_round\":3,\"member_id\":\"C3\",\"opportunity_id\":\"deliberation:3